sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Admin as Power Admin (UI)
    participant Main as Main Server
    participant DB as Main SQLite
    participant W1 as Worker 1
    participant W2 as Worker 2
    participant Wn as Worker N

    Admin->>Main: POST /API/V1/Workers/All/Update
    Main->>Main: Guard userHasAccessToPage(PushUpdatePage)
    Main->>DB: SELECT all Active WorkerNode rows

    par Push to all workers in parallel
        Main->>W1: POST /API/V1/SelfUpdate (OAuth, X-Correlation-Id)
        W1->>W1: Run self-update workflow (see 09-self-update-pointer.md)
        W1-->>Main: 200 { NewVersion: "1.5.0" }
        Main->>DB: INSERT WorkerVersion (W1, 1.5.0)
    and
        Main->>W2: POST /API/V1/SelfUpdate (OAuth, X-Correlation-Id)
        W2-->>Main: 200 { NewVersion: "1.5.0" }
        Main->>DB: INSERT WorkerVersion (W2, 1.5.0)
    and
        Main->>Wn: POST /API/V1/SelfUpdate (OAuth, X-Correlation-Id)
        Wn--xMain: 503 Unavailable
        Main->>Main: Retry exp backoff (max 3)
        Main--xAdmin: Surface partial failure for Wn
    end

    Main-->>Admin: 207 Multi-Status { successes: [W1, W2], failures: [Wn] }

    Note over Main,Wn: Single-worker variant: POST /API/V1/Workers/{id}/Update
    Note over Admin,Main: PowerShell zip publish: POST /API/V1/Workers/PublishZip<br/>then Main fans out to workers using the uploaded zip URL
